	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To the above post:  Lava storm is indeed underutilized but you need to know a few things:  <BR>
Be careful of the fire elementals and fire imps. They will gang up on you.  There is also a gypsy camp and you can fo some trading there I think.  As for Neriak, best pay for a SoW before you enter and hot foot it to Lavastorm.  Just follow the path when you enter Nektulos and do not turn left or right.  You will be pursued by a few guards but with Sow you should outpace them.  The only problem is you cannot get a bind in Lava Storm so if you die, you will need to redo the whole Sow thru Nektulos.  Also there is usually a friendly shaman in LS so you can get Sow when you need to leave.    Lastly, for you the best place to hunt would be near the entrance to Najena.  It is a safe place to zone to without any guards and hopefully no trains.  Good Luck!
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
